constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Submission of reserved matters pursuant to condition E5 of outline planning permission dated 30th March 2012, reference PA/12/00001 for 98 new homes; 500 sqm community centre; 838 sqm office space and a 954 sqm mosque (ie for building parcels A1, A2 and B within Development Zone 1, excluding Parcel R 'Phase 1A') comprising layout, scale and appearance of the buildings, the means of access thereto and the landscaping as well as approval of details of vehicular and cycle parking provision, servicing and refuse collection and associated  ancillary development.
